climateR tests

For Elyssa

Mike Johnson

library(raster)
library(climateR)
library(AOI)
AOI = aoi_get(c(45,-96,100,100),km=TRUE)

GridMet Tests

gm_pre_2006 = getGridMET(AOI, 
                         param="tmax", 
                         startDate = "2000-01-01", 
                         endDate   = "2000-01-04")
plot(gm_pre_2006[[1]])

gm_post_2006 = getGridMET(AOI, 
                          param="tmax",
                          startDate = "2010-01-01", 
                          endDate   = "2010-01-04")
plot(gm_post_2006[[1]])

MACA Tests

Historic

ma_pre_2006 = getMACA(AOI, 
                      param="tmax",
                      startDate = "2000-01-01", 
                      endDate   = "2000-01-04")
plot(ma_pre_2006[[1]])

ma_post_2006 = getMACA(AOI, 
                       param="tmax",
                       startDate = "2010-01-01", 
                       endDate   = "2010-01-04")
plot(ma_post_2006[[1]])

Future
